_sText:
(Moved to MiP as requested)

Bhop_concrete_beta1 is my first ever attempt at a map. This map took me about a week and a half to get to where it is now. I have much more planned for this map and it is far from finished. I hope you guys enjoy my creation and enjoy future creations.

Features:
- 32 spawn points
- 5 "stages"
- A concrete look that is easy on the eyes
- Great map for speedrunning
